						<summary>

						<p>This is an incomplete inscription with the beginning portion also built in. It records an endowment of land by a resident of Chandralēkai-chaturvēdimaṅgalam a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Ārkkāṭṭuk-kūṟṟam, made to the temple of Tirupperunduṟṟai-Mahādēva for rearing a flower-garden. </p>						

						</summary>
